ing: 1 (15 ounce) can whole kernel corn, drained
1/2 (8 ounce) package crumbled feta cheese with basil and sun-dried tomatoes
n: Broccoli, Corn, and Green Bean Saute
des: "Broccoli, corn, and green beans are sauteed until tender then sprinkled with flavored feta cheese."
ins: Melt the butter in a skillet over medium-high heat. Stir in broccoli, corn, and green beans. Cook until broccoli is tender. Sprinkle with feta cheese, and continue cooking until cheese is melted. Season with oregano, salt, and pepper. Serve immediately.
